{"tid":213706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遺體周二送返港】曾守明出事前演出曝光 同行鄭家生：未送院已經走咗","createTime":"2017-04-23T10:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T11:31:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9ba3e7f2e20d4be7343c623ec1eca45edbf7cc","tid":213706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170423/large/1492930020_b04a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170423%2Flarge%2F1492930020_b04a.jpg&h=c1de1de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">曾守明昨晚在廣州酒吧唱歌，台上突然不支暈倒。(網絡截圖)</span><br />\n在無綫劇集《全職沒女》中飾演房務部經理司徒健康的資深演員曾守明，兩年前曾做心臟手術激瘦，近年康復再活躍幕前，今日凌晨，他跟好友鄭家生到廣州一間酒吧登台，可是在台上突然暈倒逝，終年58歲。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今日致電同場登台、目擊事發經過的鄭家生，他說：「噚日我哋去廣州登台，中午坐朋友開車上去，全程好悠閒，去到仲食個飯，到凌晨12點先登台，我唱先，跟住介紹守明出場，我就返入後台，佢唱咗梁朝偉嗰首國語歌《你是如此難以忘記》，佢唱咗一part，跟住過音樂，佢突然跌低暈倒，我哋立即出去拉佢入後台。」<br />\n鄭家生續說：「酒吧附近有醫院，立即有醫護人員衝過嚟酒吧同佢做心外壓同急救，佢都未有送院，搓咗一輪都未有反應，守明一休克，我哋就立即聯絡佢屋企人，未有送院佢就走咗。佢暈咗冇醒過，全程昏迷，所以冇遺言，佢事發到離開一啲辛苦都冇。」<br />\n鄭家生和曾守明一齊開心登台，卻發生不幸事故，他說：「太突發性，冇辦法，佢太太同囝囝都立即上嚟，可惜今日周日都搞唔到乜嘢手續。佢兩年前心臟做咗手術，近年都康復得好好，可能當時突然病發，血揼唔到上去心臟，缺氧暈倒，我哋噚日開騷前都冇食刺激嘢，晚餐都食得好清，諗唔到會咁。」<br />\n而事發時，曾守明在場的內地好友王先生表示：「我們陪他最後一段路！他在舞台上很開心的演出，突然倒下，沒有痛苦！昨晚1:13分在舞台倒下，搶救80分鐘左右搶救無效死亡！他的家人今早6時見了他的遺體，遺容安詳。」<br />\n據王先生透露，曾守明的太太和兒子處理完手續，現正乘車返港，至於曾守明的遺體，將於周二(25日)送返香港。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170423/56602336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170423%2F56602336&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=853b6926\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170423%2F56602336&h=bfcbc7f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170423/56602336</a><br />\n<br />\n先生，篤痰係咪你吐架?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hRMkp2YJRHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhRMkp2YJRHY&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=ac135c2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hRMkp2YJRHY</a>"},{"pid":"3201d5994622d8544a50c8f3cdd75235504ef96f","tid":213706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7957834eb926acb68751350442c4982d6f5987d","tid":213706,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"你是如此難以忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲大茄<br />\n平時做小角色<br />\n但行出街真係無咩人唔識佢<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"cb3c6f16bfd09dff3414e72bed4172dddb1b2c4f","tid":213706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ba2de56164220a133cdfe8262f857d7f34f040","tid":213706,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e455be7dd3142ad9afb2dc8e843d76233aecce8","tid":213706,"uid":41695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輔警，抵死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bd256d7150dd499695ae1443dfb29c2bfeb8b3","tid":213706,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輔警，抵死</blockquote><br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899a5d7d5485621d33fb1058bc53c5d339deec9c","tid":213706,"uid":98686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"我地湖南人係唔衰得既&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede957e484c979146b1